  "body": "### Description of the Issue\r\n\r\nVersion tested: 1.0.0rc1\r\n\r\nWhen using MyCrypto offline it's not possible to sign txs for anything but the mainnet. \r\n\r\nThe reason is that it's impossible to switch to another Eth node due to the connection check preventing it. From that it follows that it's not possible to use anything else than the mainnet since the network id is coupled to the node selection.\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n- Use MyCrypto on a system without internet connection\r\n- Try to switch to anything that is not mainnet (ropsten, kovan, ...)\r\n- See that it's not possible\r\n",
